{"tid":186890,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 廣東話Kawhi Leonard主題曲 ] 馬刺的可愛（原曲：浮誇）","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T17:31:47.000Z","uid":47374,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21bbb03bac62740b8cb5f7bccfd25217952fd534","tid":186890,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yHH15cm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyHH15cm.jpg&h=8958aebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1832207810365522/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Frealcoach%2Fvideos%2F1832207810365522%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxny7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=47193935\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/realcoach/videos/1832207810365522/</a><br />\n<br />\n無辨法唔歌頌Kawhi呢個馬刺嘅巨星<br />\n可愛嘅性格、強效嘅防守、星味濃嘅進攻<br />\n加上Mark Tai 激唱嘅浮誇，請多多Share！<br />\n<br />\n記得tag朋友聽，我IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Frealbasketballcoach%2F&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxny7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=92fbfca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/realbasketballcoach/</a><br />\n-----------------<br />\n原：浮誇 (陳奕迅)<br />\n詞：正宗教練<br />\n唱：戴晉揚 Mark Tai<br />\n<br />\n以前仲細 教練發火 日日哦哦哦<br />\n我磨練夠其實會著晒火 今晚爆邊個<br />\n我臂展長 成日想去 搶你個波<br />\n偷到我又有樽鋤<br />\n球快攻 未離地 就已經 比我格咗<br />\n遇到我等於折磨<br />\n<br />\n仲練埋射三分　練嚟為咗更易打爆敵人<br />\n木獨過一生 學鄧肯寶訓<br />\n贏完唔笑嘅我至係最狠<br />\n<br />\n馬刺我大權當道 波波都知我恐怖<br />\n有敵人要突圍中路 守鬼到佢燥<br />\n時代替換唔怕　我繼續嚟開路<br />\n出啲高比嘅招數<br />\n我盡情喪射 唔用套<br />\n今晚夠數 波波無力嘈<br />\n任我轟多十零廿鋪<br />\n<br />\n第二年入playoff 罰球射失<br />\n我仲hurt過達哥<br />\n練習更加多　令熱火知錯<br />\n場場完爆你 叫我做契哥<br />\n<br />\n馬刺我大權當道 啲街坊都知我恐怖<br />\n有敵人要突圍中路 守鬼到佢燥<br />\n我決心打到老 靠我未來開路<br />\n出啲高比嘅招數<br />\n我盡情喪射 唔用套<br />\n今晚夠數 波波無力嘈<br />\n任我癲返十零廿鋪<br />\n<br />\n成隊勇士夠膽砌多鋪<br />\n快睇我Solo 我苦練完實進步<br />\n盡全力殺埋入下個Final"},{"pid":"e70d83a8d68fa5a38a58e1fcc7534d0adf19942d","tid":186890,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"23995db87ba106e91e419628f6a5d9095dda279e","tid":186890,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推！</blockquote><br />\nhi 柒叔"},{"pid":"6ce18c3326f77d6191bbd5ec5ba0d3618eb1f48c","tid":186890,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推！</blockquote><br />\nhi 柒叔</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fafa4502ae85c0c9789bb7dc3e363cbb822290","tid":186890,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:18:01.000Z","msg":"贏完唔笑既我至係最狠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鐘意kawhi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cb834ae1d266b3fa8ef28c100beed591b9eb9a","tid":186890,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>贏完唔笑既我至係最狠！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鐘意kawhi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n低調但又有星味，好高境界"},{"pid":"fc04883263aa23f1fecbf2736a23b260cdca26c0","tid":186890,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:41:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7d979490788653a0ce484f83f2f52be19e36d955","tid":186890,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6a20dfb3f7178ea009e9c70dc780a8d807f95066","tid":186890,"uid":4737